data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE, SUNDAY FEBRUARY 4th from 2-4 pm*** Welcome to 112 Amistad Blvd in Universal City - a 3-bed, 2-bath single story home with a perfect blend of style and functionality. As you enter, the spacious living room greets you with its vaulted ceilings, with the focal point of the room being a cozy gas fireplace. The kitchen features an open layout, with an abundance of counter space, a built-in oven, and a flat cooktop. Recently upgraded in 2023 is the oven and dishwasher, ensuring modern convenience and efficiency for your daily needs. The master suite is a retreat in itself, strategically positioned away from the secondary bedrooms for added privacy. It boasts a generously sized layout, complete with a walk-in closet and a full bath featuring a walk-in shower. The secondary bedrooms are thoughtfully designed with ample closet space, ensuring comfort and functionality. The property also offers a second full bath to accommodate the needs of family and guests.  In 2023, an upgraded HVAC system with a UV light was installed, providing enhanced air quality and comfort throughout the home.  Step outside to discover additional features that make this property stand out. A gated front porch adds a touch of charm and privacy, while the covered patio in the back offers a perfect spot for outdoor gatherings. Enjoy the shade provided by mature trees in the yard, surrounded by a privacy fence for a sense of seclusion. Practical features include plumbing for a water softener and garage door opener. Location is convenient to Loop 1604, IH-35, Randolph AFB, The Forum Shopping, Costco, IKEA, HEB, restaurants and so much more.
